CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 25, 1961, pg. B5 reads: "More Than 300 Attend Chi Dance - Among the more than 300 guests attending the smart Chi Delta Mu Fraternity supper dance last Saturday evening at the Pittsburgh Hilton was the above group...in the center photo are, clockwise, Dr. and Mrs. Harry Wechler, Dr. and Mrs. Horace Christian, Dr. L. R. Downing, Mrs. M.R. Hadley, Dr. Albert Reiter, Mrs. Reiter, Dr. Hadley and Mrs. R. L. Vann..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, clockwise: Dr. and Mrs. Harry Wechler, Dr. and Mrs. Horace Christian, Dr. L. R. Downing, Mrs. M.R. Hadley, Dr. and Mrs. Albert Reiter, Dr. Hadley, and Jessie Vann, seated at banquet table in Hilton Hotel for Chi Delta Mu supper dance
